#text=I was living in Austin Texas and decided I was going to try my luck at making a cake .
#text=I researched a few to try out .
#text=The first one that I made was a layered Italian cake with white frosting and coconut flakes .
#text=This one took a lot of effort due to the multiple layers , but the taste ended up being excellent .
#text=I thought I would try my luck next with a chocolate ganash frosting on top of a peanut butter cake .
#text=This cake came out better tasting in my opinion and the in the opinion of others .
#text=For the peanut butter portion of it , it had peanut butter mixed with actual butter baked on top of a graham cracker compressed crust .
#text=The ganash was made from melting chocolate in heavy whipping cream briefly in the microwave and spreading over .
#text=Once cooled it made kind of a shell on top of the peanut butter .
